
[ ] Room Management
  [ ] If a client is already in a room:
    [ ] Do not show them the option to create another one
    [ ] Do not attempt to add the client to another room
    [ ] Display room key
  [ ] If a client is not in a room:
    [ ] Show the option to create a room
    [ ] Show the option to join a room
  [ ] When no clients left in a room, or room age > 2 hours, delete the room
  [ ] When two clients are in the room, show the users a "Begin" button
  [ ] If one player leaves the room, keep the room.
    [ ] If another player joins, replace old player with new

[ ] Game Screen
  [ ] Show end game button